---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import logo from '@/assets/images/favicon.png';
---

<section
  class="flex flex-col p-6 pt-32 justify-center items-center text-center text-black min-h-screen rounded-b-[4rem]"
>
  <h1 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-calistoga">
    Silvia's story behind Earth Mama's Kitchen
  </h1>

  <p class="text-lg md:text-xl mt-6 max-w-3xl font-semibold leading-relaxed">
    Earth Mama's Kitchen is a portfolio case study inspired by Silvia's original
    bakery story. This website does not represent a business currently operated
    by Silvia.
  </p>

  <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl mt-6 max-w-3xl">
    What began as a small passion in Silvia's kitchen slowly became something
    more meaningful. The story was never just about desserts — it was about
    creating something beautiful with patience, creativity, and love.
    <br /><br />

    Every cupcake bouquet is carefully piped by hand and inspired by real
    flowers. The original bakery story turns simple ingredients into edible art
    that can brighten someone's day and make special moments even sweeter.
    <br /><br />

    <strong>Baking is more than food — it is a way of sharing joy.</strong>
  </p>
  <figure class="mt-10 flex justify-center">
    <Image
      src={logo}
      alt="Earth Mama Kitchen logo"
      width={256}
      sizes="16rem"
      loading="lazy"
      class="w-64"
    />
  </figure>
</section>

